        <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0723/0527/9273/files/instagram-solid-icon.png?v=1683005211" alt="Instagram Icon">
        <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0723/0527/9273/files/whatsapp-solid-icon.png?v=1683005211" alt="WhatsApp Icon">
